323
01:04:09,240 --> 01:04:13,233
his parents came back

324
01:04:15,640 --> 01:04:20,120
We didn't know
how to explain it to them

325
01:04:20,120 --> 01:04:25,069
They wouldn't listen

326
01:04:25,200 --> 01:04:32,117
They just kept blaming us

327
01:04:37,960 --> 01:04:45,150
And where did you go
all that night?

328
01:04:49,200 --> 01:04:55,230
That night we decided
to go back to the temple

329
01:04:57,800 --> 01:05:01,634
But Uan

330
01:05:05,880 --> 01:05:14,879
Uan had this stupid idea.

331
01:05:23,280 --> 01:05:26,716
This is the safest place.

332
01:05:26,840 --> 01:05:30,071
Aren't you going to keep it
for the ritual.

333
01:05:32,720 --> 01:05:35,951
Let's just get past tonight

334
01:05:36,080 --> 01:05:39,117
lt'll be kind of like being reborn

335
01:05:44,040 --> 01:05:47,316
Don't think of me in a bad way

336
01:05:47,440 --> 01:05:50,079
I'm asking you

337
01:05:51,680 --> 01:05:52,999
Nui

338
01:05:53,120 --> 01:05:54,160
What?

339
01:05:54,160 --> 01:05:58,392
Close the coffin for me.

340
01:05:58,480 --> 01:06:00,152
Okay.

341
01:07:11,640 --> 01:07:12,117
Uan, wake up.

342
01:07:12,240 --> 01:07:13,070
Uan.

343
01:07:13,200 --> 01:07:15,156
Uan.

344
01:07:19,680 --> 01:07:23,309
Uan.

345
01:07:33,920 --> 01:07:37,037
The reason for his death.

346
01:07:37,160 --> 01:07:40,470
We believe it to be caused by
lack of oxygen

347
01:07:40,600 --> 01:07:42,989
But what do you expect from
someone stupid enough

348
01:07:43,120 --> 01:07:47,511
to sleep in a coffin with
the lid closed

349
01:07:49,360 --> 01:07:53,638
But actually he didn't close
it all the way

350
01:07:56,360 --> 01:07:58,874
He left an opening
for air to breathe.

351
01:08:49,200 --> 01:08:52,749
There's only the two of us left.

352
01:09:01,800 --> 01:09:06,078
Pim, would you like to meet
Saeng Daow?

353
01:09:09,120 --> 01:09:13,238
How? This is not a living
human being.

354
01:09:15,040 --> 01:09:20,034
Are we just going to wait for her
to come to us?

355
01:09:22,040 --> 01:09:25,874
But where can we find her?

356
01:09:29,080 --> 01:09:32,231
We'll start from the place
where she was murdered.

357
01:12:00,800 --> 01:12:08,514
He cut off her head and tied her
hair to the air condition vent.

358
01:12:24,160 --> 01:12:29,314
Did you see anything strange?

359
01:12:31,680 --> 01:12:34,478
No, none at all.

360
01:12:37,640 --> 01:12:43,237
Here, that's all that is left

361
01:12:49,920 --> 01:12:55,870
Oh, there is one thing that
you should know

362
01:13:10,200 --> 01:13:19,598
Saeng Daow was pregnant
when she died.

363
01:13:32,400 --> 01:13:35,995
The letter that the hotel
employee gave us

364
01:13:36,120 --> 01:13:38,953
was written by Saeng Daow

365
01:13:39,080 --> 01:13:41,514
but was never sent

366
01:13:43,280 --> 01:13:45,271
We decided to go to the address

367
01:13:45,400 --> 01:13:47,755
that was on the front of
the envelope

368
01:13:47,880 --> 01:13:52,078
and deliver that letter

369
01:13:55,160 --> 01:13:58,391
hoping that it might
release her from this pain

370
01:13:58,480 --> 01:14:03,873
and suffering she is in.

371
01:16:22,280 --> 01:16:24,714
Who let you in?

372
01:16:28,120 --> 01:16:30,315
I'm sorry

373
01:17:02,120 --> 01:17:04,429
Excuse me Ma'am

374
01:17:05,120 --> 01:17:09,352
Ma'amThe name on this letter
is addressed to you, right?

375
01:17:20,160 --> 01:17:23,232
It's a letter from Saeng Daow.

376
01:17:42,200 --> 01:17:44,873
Saeng Daow

377
01:17:44,960 --> 01:17:48,430
Saeng Daow my child

378
01:18:33,400 --> 01:18:38,838
Saeng Daow ran away
from home a long time ago

379
01:18:38,920 --> 01:18:41,878
I never received any news
from her

380
01:18:41,960 --> 01:18:46,120
I didn't know where to find her

381
01:18:46,120 --> 01:18:50,193
Her father died
when she was just a child

382
01:18:50,280 --> 01:18:58,710
I raised her with the money
from my new husband.

383
01:19:08,440 --> 01:19:12,991
Who's the girl standing
next to Saeng Daow?

384
01:19:13,120 --> 01:19:14,997
Oh, that's Tawan

385
01:19:15,120 --> 01:19:18,120
My other daughter

386
01:19:18,120 --> 01:19:21,160
Saeng Daow loved her sister
very much

387
01:19:21,160 --> 01:19:26,075
They went everywhere together,
never were separated

388
01:19:26,200 --> 01:19:34,517
Tawan was close to her sister,
she cried wanting to go too

389
01:19:35,240 --> 01:19:43,238
Saeng Daow just ran away
and didn't tell anyone

390
01:19:43,360 --> 01:19:48,354
She left her sister even though
they've never been apart

391
01:19:48,480 --> 01:19:56,160
Tawan must've been really lonely.

392
01:19:57,440 --> 01:20:01,638
And what happened to Tawan?

393
01:20:01,720 --> 01:20:06,874
Tawan would just keep herself
in the room

394
01:20:06,960 --> 01:20:19,031
Everytime I saw her
she would be sleeping here

395
01:20:19,160 --> 01:20:24,951
I never thought that one day
she wouldn't wake up

396
01:20:38,040 --> 01:20:40,508
Who's in the next room?

397
01:20:40,640 --> 01:20:43,108
That's just my husband

398
01:20:43,200 --> 01:20:44,189
He's probably hungry

399
01:20:44,280 --> 01:20:48,034
Go on

400
01:20:48,160 --> 01:20:50,071
It's getting dark, I think the
both of you should be going

401
01:20:50,160 --> 01:20:54,073
It's dangerous driving back
at night

402
01:20:55,120 --> 01:20:59,432
Go on now

403
01:21:05,680 --> 01:21:06,635
Go on

404
01:21:06,720 --> 01:21:09,120
It's nothing

405
01:21:09,120 --> 01:21:10,792
Go, go, go, go

406
01:21:10,920 --> 01:21:15,038
And don't come back

407
01:21:35,880 --> 01:21:45,915
I'm sorry Saeng Daow.

408
01:22:32,240 --> 01:22:38,554
So, we still don't know
anything, right?

409
01:22:41,960 --> 01:22:47,273
Why is Saeng Daow
so angry at us?

410
01:22:47,400 --> 01:22:51,757
It might not have anything
to do with us at all

411
01:22:51,880 --> 01:22:54,348
She probably just doesn't like us.

412
01:22:54,440 --> 01:22:59,230
And wants to kill us
because she's crazy

413
01:23:06,040 --> 01:23:08,315
So, what now?

414
01:23:09,360 --> 01:23:11,476
You want to go back and sleep
in the coffin?

415
01:23:11,600 --> 01:23:13,477
So, I can die the same way Uan did?

416
01:23:13,600 --> 01:23:15,670
No, thanks

417
01:23:15,800 --> 01:23:18,234
We'll just let the Buddhist do
the ritual for us first

418
01:23:18,360 --> 01:23:21,511
It might work.

419
01:23:25,880 --> 01:23:30,032
Don't you want to know more
about Saeng Daow?

420
01:23:30,160 --> 01:23:35,029
The more we know
the faster we die

421
01:23:36,640 --> 01:23:41,430
Oh... Did you see anything
over at her house?

422
01:23:46,040 --> 01:23:49,077
Like what?

423
01:23:52,720 --> 01:23:55,154
Like under the bed?

424
01:26:32,000 --> 01:26:33,991
Sa... SaSa

425
