Pim...

456
01:31:26,840 --> 01:31:29,070
I don't know
what else to ask you

457
01:31:29,200 --> 01:31:34,832
All your responses just end up
back on the same story

458
01:31:34,920 --> 01:31:38,708
It's because of a ghost

459
01:31:40,480 --> 01:31:46,589
Alright then,
what about your friend?

460
01:31:46,680 --> 01:31:49,990
Where is he?

461
01:31:53,400 --> 01:31:57,120
We had a difference of opinions...

462
01:31:57,120 --> 01:31:58,473
He thought that the Buddhist
priest would be able to release him

463
01:31:58,600 --> 01:32:02,878
from the curse by performing
the ritual

464
01:32:02,960 --> 01:32:11,311
So, he went back to the temple to
try the ritual one more time.

465
01:32:12,920 --> 01:32:14,911
What about you?

466
01:32:15,040 --> 01:32:19,033
Don't you think of doing
the same?

467
01:32:21,000 --> 01:32:29,430
If I did I probably wouldn't be
here now telling you about it.

468
01:32:30,840 --> 01:32:37,518
Because from then on,
Nui just disappeared.

469
01:32:39,680 --> 01:32:45,789
To this day, I still can't find him.

470
01:32:49,680 --> 01:32:56,756
Your story is quite unbelievable

471
01:32:58,720 --> 01:33:02,679
It's creepier than any book
I've read

472
01:33:03,120 --> 01:33:12,950
But your characters seem to
have the same names as mine

473
01:33:16,280 --> 01:33:19,477
I'll tell you what

474
01:33:19,960 --> 01:33:23,077
I'll tell you a story of my own

475
01:33:23,200 --> 01:33:28,832
I had a suspect here once,
waiting for interrogation

476
01:33:28,920 --> 01:33:32,151
He was a psycho

477
01:33:32,240 --> 01:33:39,396
We believed he killed people
as a sacrificial offering

478
01:33:39,480 --> 01:33:41,471
What ever that is

479
01:33:41,600 --> 01:33:43,120
Later that night,
he tore his clothes off

480
01:33:43,120 --> 01:33:46,271
and hung himself on the jail bars

481
01:33:46,400 --> 01:33:58,358
There was a writing
on the wall written in blood

482
01:33:59,240 --> 01:34:05,190
He might be the murderer
in your story

483
01:34:06,120 --> 01:34:13,276
So, do you still see Saeng Daow?

484
01:34:16,400 --> 01:34:21,076
Is she here now?

485
01:34:26,440 --> 01:34:30,399
Anyway, you're probably tired

486
01:34:30,480 --> 01:34:33,074
You can go

487
01:34:38,720 --> 01:34:39,994
but I'll still need you to come back

488
01:34:40,120 --> 01:34:43,157
and make your statement
one more time

489
01:34:43,480 --> 01:34:49,112
I hope you'll cooperate.

490
01:35:15,880 --> 01:35:21,591
If the same thing happened to you

491
01:35:25,240 --> 01:35:32,237
You might not ever want
to see anyone again.

492
01:35:39,960 --> 01:35:42,918
With all do love and respect to
my dearest mother.

493
01:35:43,040 --> 01:35:46,715
I'm so sorry that I ran away
without telling anyone.

494
01:35:46,840 --> 01:35:50,515
I know it must've caused
you much pain and sorrow.

495
01:35:50,640 --> 01:35:55,873
But did you know that this
daughter also felt the same pain

496
01:35:55,960 --> 01:36:00,078
and sorrow as you did?

497
01:36:00,200 --> 01:36:07,072
All I could do was cry
for what I've done to you.

498
01:36:07,160 --> 01:36:09,674
I'm such a bad person

499
01:36:09,800 --> 01:36:13,713
for leaving you and my sister
isn't that right mother?

500
01:36:13,840 --> 01:36:15,717
But please believe me mother.

501
01:36:15,840 --> 01:36:21,198
I have my reasons in making
this decision.

502
01:36:21,280 --> 01:36:24,158
If I had to stay
in that house any longer

503
01:36:24,240 --> 01:36:25,992
my life would surely be filled
with such heartache

504
01:36:26,120 --> 01:36:29,874
and would finally end
without meaning.

505
01:36:29,960 --> 01:36:34,158
Please don't ask me
to go back to that house

506
01:36:34,240 --> 01:36:38,950
because I don't think
I have the courage to face you

507
01:36:39,080 --> 01:36:42,120
or anyone ever again.

508
01:36:42,120 --> 01:36:49,037
My sins can never be erased
for as long as I live

509
01:36:49,160 --> 01:36:55,918
and I will never forget the people
that have done me wrong...

510
01:36:56,040 --> 01:37:04,948
especially those men which
to this day I curse them all.

511
01:37:05,080 --> 01:37:06,957
In conclusion

512
01:37:07,080 --> 01:37:10,868
I ask you to please explain to
Tawan so that she understands

513
01:37:10,960 --> 01:37:13,918
because I really worry about her.

514
01:37:14,040 --> 01:37:16,474
She is still so young

515
01:37:16,600 --> 01:37:20,036
and probably very disappointed
in me for what I've done.

516
01:37:20,160 --> 01:37:23,038
With Love, Saeng Daow

